<h3>Stock Performance</h3>

<% array = [] %>
<% @holdings.each do |holding| %>
<% array << holding.dollar_value %>
<% end %>
<% assets = array.sum %>

<table class="table table-condensed table-hover">

  <thead>

  <tr>
    <th colspan = "3"></th>
    <th></th>
    <th colspan = "8" style="text-align:center; border-bottom:1px solid;">Performance*</th>

  </tr>

  <tr>
    <th>Sector</th>
    <th>Symbol</th>
    <th>Weight</th>
    <th> </th>
    <th>Start Date</th>
    <th>YTD</th>
    <th>Start Date</th>
    <th>1-Yr.</th>
    <th>Start Date</th>
    <th>3-Yr.</th>
    <th>Start Date</th>
    <th>5-Yr.</th>
  </tr>

  </thead>

  <tbody>
  <% @holdings.each do |holding| %>
  <tr>
    <td><%= holding.sector_name_for_holdings %></td>
    <td><%= link_to "#{holding.symbol}", "http://www.google.com/finance?q=#{holding.symbol}", :target => "_blank" %></td>
    <td style="text-align:right">
      <%= holding.weight(@assets) %>
    </td>
    <td></td>
    <td style="text-align:right"><%= holding.end_of_last_year_date %></td>
    <td style="text-align:right"><%= Format.percent_dec(holding.ytd_performance) %></td>
    <td style="text-align:right"><%= holding.one_year_ago_date %></td>
    <td style="text-align:right"><%= Format.percent_dec(holding.one_year_performance) %></td>
    <td style="text-align:right"><%= holding.three_years_ago_date %></td>
    <td style="text-align:right"><%= Format.percent_dec(holding.three_year_performance) %></td>
    <td style="text-align:right"><%= holding.five_years_ago_date %></td>
    <td style="text-align:right"><%= Format.percent_dec(holding.five_year_performance) %></td>
  </tr>
  <% end %>
  </tbody>
</table>
<em>*Intended to be one, three, and five year performance, but if available history is shorter, the actual start date of the performance calculated is indicated.  YTD and 1-yr. are straight calculations while 3-yr. and 5-yr. are CAGR adjusted.</em>
